Package: regions
Title: Processing Regional Statistics
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Daniel",
           family = "Antal",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "adaniel@freemail.hu",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-7513-6760"))
Description: Validating sub-national statistical typologies, recoding across 
    standard typologies of sub-national statistics, and making valid aggregate
    level imputation, re-aggregation, re-weighting and projection down to 
    lower hierachical levels to create meaningful meaningful
    data panels and time series. 
    See regions.danielantal.eu for more information.
